05/12/2010
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- The opposition Social Democratic Alliance of Macedonia (SDSM) is holding a rally in Skopje on Sunday (December 5th) against the government for policies the opposition says isolate Macedonia and increase poverty. The SDSM is expecting 50,000 people to join them from across the country; 15 opposition parties support the march. (Makfax, Inpress, Alsat, MIA, Deutsche Welle - 05/12/10)
